snippet.title: Super Mario 64 Arguably Better Edition - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a Super Mario 64 hack that fixes and updates various things, such as the camera, the controls, and wall jumping!

You can view a full list of what's changed, and download the patch from here:
https://mfgg.net/index.php?act=resdb&param=02&c=7&id=36500

The music used is by GaMetal, and the footage is recorded by GTM. This hack wouldn't be possible without the SM64 Decompilation project!
